<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>شهادة إتمام</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        html, body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .certificate {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            position: relative;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 0;
            box-shadow: none;
            padding: 40px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #a5b4fc;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        .logo {
            width: 110px;
            height: auto;
            filter: drop-shadow(2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3));
        }
        .content {
            text-align: center;
            flex-grow: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #e0e7ff;
        }
        .content .name {
            font-size: 2.8em;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 10px 0;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border-bottom: 2px solid #60a5fa;
            display: inline-block;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            max-width: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        .content .course {
            font-size: 1.6em;
            color: #bfdbfe;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 8px 0;
            max-width: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        .footer-section {
            padding-top: 10px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        .signature-area {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0 10px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .verification-info {
            text-align: right;
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #93c5fd;
            max-width: 40%;
        }
        .signature-box {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 50%;
        }
        .signature-line {
            width: 180px;
            height: 70px;
            margin: 0 auto 5px;
        }
        .signature-line img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: contain;
            filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
        }
        .signature-box p {
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #bfdbfe;
            line-height: 1.4;
            max-width: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        .signature-box .title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }
        .date-section {
            text-align: right;
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #93c5fd;
            padding: 0 10px;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="certificate">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>شهادة إتمام</h1>
            <img src="https://i.ibb.co/x8sYjYyK/out.png" alt="شعار الأكاديمية" class="logo">
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>تشهد أكاديمية العرب التقنية بأن</p>
            <div class="name"><%= userName %></div>
            <p>قد أتم بنجاح متطلبات</p>
            <div class="course"><%= courseName %></div>
            <p>وهي مبادرة تعليمية تهدف إلى تطوير المهارات التقنية في العالم العربي.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer-section">
            <div class="signature-area">
                <div class="verification-info">
                    <p><strong>رقم التحقق:</strong></p>
                    <p><%= certificateId %></p>
                    <p><strong>تاريخ الإصدار:</strong> <%= issueDate %></p>
                </div>
                <div class="signature-box">
                    <div class="signature-line">
                        <img src="https://i.ibb.co/1Jqbrryd/1757739208029.png" alt="توقيع المدير">
                    </div>
                    <p class="title">محمد ال عبية</p>
                    <p>مشرف البرنامج</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>